item.title: CVE-2021-20348|2024-08-03T17:37:23.716Z -- ibm -- rational%20rhapsody%20model%20manager
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation and IBM Engineering products are vulnerable to server-side request forgery (SSRF). This may allow an authenticated attacker to send unauthorized requests from the system, potentially leading to network enumeration or facilitating other attacks. IBM X-ForceID: 194597.
